{"tid":1359832,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲籍香港人可以點幫手","createTime":"2019-07-24T08:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T18:44:33.000Z","uid":288067,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c1d8d23057c80ccd0127925d1dc3e047c129a134","tid":1359832,"uid":288067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"香港人努力奮勇自強,也要繼盡力尋求任何向外國求援機會<br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會前排一致通過支持港人訴求(除了林鄭下台一項),持歐盟國籍的香港人作為選民,有權要求歐洲議會加大力度<br />\n<br />\n向金鐘香港歐盟辦事處好,向歐洲相關部門方面也好,請教各位有識之士,歐洲藉香港人可以點幫手?<br />\n趁英國未脫歐,香港人應該可以團結到好多好多歐盟公民<br />\n<br />\n看到721上環元朗之後非常悲憤,覺得尋找機會要有殺錯冇放過大包圍<br />\n<br />\n懇請有識之士賜教籌組<br />\n香港人彈藥庫始終是連登<br />\n謝謝"},{"pid":"89d5fb013ecee130c2c6d906386e9265d59e4e05","tid":1359832,"uid":276839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"幫唔到，除非香港正接令佢地揾到勁多錢。"},{"pid":"0b8bfb604450adebc5a8cbb46f847bc7bf248edd","tid":1359832,"uid":70574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9a874b837cfe60bedf26f9f93ec6a5484ef1ea","tid":1359832,"uid":182334,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:59:57.000Z","msg":"放棄歐洲藉"},{"pid":"16415591bd5279858f0fb223781a64bbc3ad52b1","tid":1359832,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de9a874b837cfe60bedf26f9f93ec6a5484ef1ea","tid":1359832,"uid":182334,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:59:57.000Z","msg":"放棄歐洲藉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b679b22d097082749dae3df081b9a06e10726b6","tid":1359832,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:03:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68c382ffe2a4ec766cb8503d779fa7dafd22265e","tid":1359832,"uid":225828,"like":0,"di